{"article_id":"wVNk2H2jUjvvv6tC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The White House is considering making the argument","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that President Trump has not officially been impeached ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"given that House Speaker Nancy Pelosi has not transmitted the articles of impeachment to the Senate ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"two sources","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"involved in the president 's impeachment defense","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"told .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The House voted to impeach Mr. Trump on two articles of impeachment","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"- abuse of power and obstruction of Congress -","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"However , Pelosi told reporters on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that the House would wait to deliver the articles","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"until the Senate had laid out the rules for the trial .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"`` When we see the process","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"that 's set forth in the Senate ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"then we 'll know the number of managers","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"we 'll have to move forward ,","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"and who we would choose , ''","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"the California Democrat said .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"The House must vote on a resolution","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"designating impeachment managers","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"to prosecute the case against Mr. Trump in the Senate","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"before delivering the articles .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"The White House is considering making the case","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that Mr. Trump has not been impeached","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"based on an opinion piece by Harvard Law Professor Noah Feldman on Bloomberg 's opinion page Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Feldman was one of the legal experts","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"called by Democrats","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"to testify before the House Judiciary Committee earlier this month","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"and has advocated for Mr. Trump 's impeachment and removal from office .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"`` Impeachment","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"as contemplated by the Constitution","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"does not consist merely of the vote by the House ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"but of the process","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"of sending the articles to the Senate for trial , ''","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Feldman wrote in Bloomberg .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"`` Both parts are necessary","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"to make an impeachment under the Constitution :","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"The House must actually send the articles","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"and send managers to the Senate","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"to prosecute the impeachment .","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"And the Senate must actually hold a trial . ''","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"`` If the House does not communicate its impeachment to the Senate ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"it has n't actually impeached the president .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"If the articles are not transmitted ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Trump could legitimately say","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"that he was n't truly impeached at all , ''","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"Feldman wrote .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"However , Harvard Law Professor Laurence Tribe wrote on Twitter","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that he disagreed with Feldman 's analysis ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that `` under Art . I , Sec . 2 , Clause 5 , he was impeached on Dec 18 , 2019 .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"He will forever remain impeached .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"Period . ''","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"That portion of the Constitution says","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"that the House of Representatives `` shall have the sole Power of Impeachment . ''","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"The sources told","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that the White House views Pelosi 's delay as `` a Christmas gift . ''","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"They plan to use the delay","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"to argue","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that the Democrats have so little faith in their own case for impeachment ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"they are too scared to trigger a trial","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"they know","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"they will lose .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"The two sources also say","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"that the president ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"while `` angry '' about what he views as an unfair process ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"is actually in a `` very good mood , ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"and feels confident","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"he can win the messaging war via Twitter","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"while lawmakers are back home for the holidays .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"A senior White House official said","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"the White House might pursue that line of messaging ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"but the White House is also in a `` wait and see '' attitude over the Christmas holiday .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Right now ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"the official said","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"they preferred to focus on `` happy '' messaging , not `` flogging '' impeachment messaging over the holidays .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Republicans in Congress are already making this argument .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell said in a speech on the Senate floor Thursday","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"that Pelosi 's decision","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"to withhold the articles from the Senate","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"shows","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Democrats `` may be too afraid to even transmit their shoddy work product to the Senate . ''","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"House Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy echoed those comments :","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"`` She 's admitting defeat","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"by not sending them .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"By refusing to send impeachment over ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"she knows","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"its outcome is not good . ''","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Pelosi and Democrats in the House and Senate are trying to pressure the Senate to call for more documents and for witnesses","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"who did not testify in the House impeachment proceedings","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"because the White House prevented them from appearing .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"`` I told leader McConnell","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"that we would not support any trial","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"without witnesses or documents , ''","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"House Minority Leader Chuck Schumer said Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"Mr. Trump 's legislative director told","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"that Mr. Trump is `` baffled '' by the possibility","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"that Pelosi might withhold articles of impeachment from the Senate for an extended period of time .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"`` I think","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"the president is completely baffled at the theory","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"that Nancy Pelosi appears to have","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"that somehow holding back impeachment articles will leverage some sort of specific behavior out of the Senate , ''","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Eric Ueland told chief Washington Correspondent Major Garrett in an interview for `` The Takeout '' podcast .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"Ueland suggested","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"that holding the articles could be `` constitutionally questionable . ''","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"He also said","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"it would be `` extraordinarily unprecedented ''","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"if articles were to be withheld","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"in order to force a legislative outcome .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"In a rare interview","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"that will air Sunday ,","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"the president 's daughter , Ivanka Trump , told `` Face the Nation '' moderator Margaret Brennan","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"that her father was `` energized '' by his impeachment ,","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"which she called `` the first purely partisan impeachment . ''","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"Still , Ueland and White House counsel Pat Cipollone were offered the opportunity","depth":3},{"id":115,"text":"to tour the Senate floor ,","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"which would serve as a courtroom ,","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"and check out the support spaces behind the scenes .","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"They also have the chance","depth":3},{"id":119,"text":"to be introduced to people","depth":4},{"id":120,"text":"who are there every day","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"when the Senate is in session ,","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"and would be for any Senate trial .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":245,"left":236,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":217,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":177,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":128,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":125,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":2,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":143,"right":175,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":139,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":130,"right":138,"relati